snippet.title: Paper Mario Black Pit - F3 2020 Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
I have been working on this mod for around 14 months, there's still a lot of things that need to be done but I hope you like it 😄

Demo Download:
https://www.mediafire.com/file/cqjh7d4z2q92pfs/BlackPit_Demo_v0.2.1.bps/file
Patcher (patch onto Paper Mario US z64 ROM):
https://hack64.net/tools/patcher.php

Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/eldexter

You can also join the Paper Mario Modding Discord server for more stuff about this and other PM mods in the making:
https://discord.gg/pUWj6ss

Remember to subscribe to this channel for more Paper Mario N64 Mods 😉

The logo, title screen, and the 20th Anniversary Badge was made by Kevin Arthur, remember to follow him on twitter too 😉
https://twitter.com/KevinArthurLS
